# agent-delivery-kit

- Read root `AGENTS.md` and `product.yaml` before work.
- Default is code-first: implement high-quality changes; do not drive task state machines unless asked.
- Pre-coding: `docs/code-quality-prerequisites.md`.
- Delivery mode: `docs/delivery-workflow.md` + `ruby scripts/deliver.rb <task>`.
- Product facts live in `docs/requirements.md`, architecture, OpenAPI, database — not in the kit.
